    -   Description: Delete a user (Admin only).
    -   Path Params: `userId` (string/int).
    -   Authentication: Required (Admin role).
    -   Responses:
        -   `204 No Content`.
        -   `401 Unauthorized`/`403 Forbidden`.
        -   `404 Not Found`.

